name: End of Summer BBQ Golden Gardens
description: It's that time again, Our 5th Annual BBQ. These are very relaxing events and so much fun. Bring people, Bring whatever you would like. Some people Bake some people Grill, Anything goes. Coffee beforehand at Jibe Espresso Bar (good meeting spot) What we always need:plates, forks, napkins, and charcoal. Games, Beer, Lawn chairs always a perfect idea. Let's unwind and enjoy the end of summer. Can't wait you guys...
